---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Who We Are">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Who We Are</h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            Lake Ozark Christian Church is a community of faith that is dedicated to sharing the Gospel of Jesus Christ. 
            All are welcome in our congregation, for Christ's table is open to all. Our faith is not simply a set of beliefs, 
            but a way of life as we share the light of our Savior with the world.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Beliefs -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Beliefs</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We look to the Word of God for inspiration, guidance, comfort, and challenge.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We believe in a God who is still saving lives, still working for peace and justice, still surprising us with miraculous wonder.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We believe in a God who invites us to share in the ministry of Jesus Christ, through service to our neighbor.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Mission -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Our Lord calls us out to care for others—to love God and neighbor, and to work for a better world through service, 
            mission, and prophetic witness.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-brand pl-4 italic text-gray-600">
            "To bring Good News to the poor … proclaim release to the captives and recovery of sight to the blind, 
            to let the oppressed go free, to proclaim the year of the Lord's favor." (Luke 4:18-19)
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Journey -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Journey Together</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We believe in a God who invites us to grow as disciples. We are all on a journey, but God is always calling us 
            out to be more than we are, to follow in the footsteps of Jesus Christ, to grow in faith and service and love. 
            Our Lord walks with us that we might find meaning in our lives and make a difference in the lives of others. 
            We offer safe space where people of all ages can explore, grow, and learn about God and the Christian faith.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Affiliation -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-600">
            We are affiliated with the Christian Church (Disciples of Christ),<br>
            "A movement for wholeness in a fragmented world."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>